        "text_NUULqj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> is a simple, reliable core sampling tool designed to accurately measure grease, solids, and sludge levels in <strong>grease traps, interceptors, septic tanks, clarifiers</strong>, and <strong>sludge pits</strong>. Easy to use and highly effective, it's widely trusted by pretreatment professionals across the United States.</p><p>These industry experts rely on the <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> when they need precise, consistent, and legally defensible measurements of <strong>FOG (Fats, Oils, and Grease)</strong> in systems like grease traps, interceptors, lift stations, and sludge pits. Its accuracy and repeatability make it the preferred choice for regulatory compliance and routine monitoring.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
